ons of white dwarfs\nslowly brought to the Chandrasekhar limit---which should also occur---are\nresponsible for some of the \"atypical\" type Ia supernovae.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2010 22:45:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jun 2010 18:40:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 11 Sep 2010 01:18:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
