rac fermions appear in the edge of the systems and charge fractionalization\noccurs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jun 2010 11:55:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Sep 2010 07:09:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-12-13"}
